review: We did antidote and it was very well thought out. Can't wait to go again!

room_title: Escape room "Antidote" by Escapology Memphis in Memphis
review: Was my first escape room experience and it was amazing! I will be back again for sure! We survived the virus outbreak! Amazing ambiance and props. Strongly recommend! And go on Sunday, not as booked then.

room_title: Escape room "Antidote" by Escapology Memphis in Memphis
review: If you've been to any other escape rooms in town, you'll find that Escapology will be a definite UPGRADE! This place is high above the others in detail, decor, staff, and game excitement. We did antidote and it was awesome. We will be back to do the other rooms very soon!
